OL,4,G1410FFour in a Bed
OL,5,     GThe competition kicks off at The
OL,6,     GUnicorn Inn in Ludlow, where Zoe
OL,7,     Gand Lee hope that their
OL,8,     Gglamorous, fairy-tale rooms will
OL,9,     Gbecome the stuff of legend. And
OL,10,     GZoe wows the guests at breakfast.
OL,11,G1440FFour in a Bed
OL,12,     GThe second visit is to the East
OL,13,     GWalls Hotel in Chichester, which
OL,14,     Gowners Celia and Damon describe
OL,15,     Gas 'bespoke'. Their guests go
OL,16,     Gcrazy for the continental, but
OL,17,     Gthere's loo brush controversy.
