OL,4,G1510FFour in a Bed
OL,5,     GThere's toilet brush controversy
OL,6,     Gfor the second time in the week.
OL,7,     GAnd the battle of the bangers
OL,8,     Gcontinues, as ambitious Jake and
OL,9,     GChris welcome their rivals to The
OL,10,     GWheatsheaf in Cheshire.
OL,11,G1540FFour in a Bed
OL,12,     GThe final visit is to Shawries
OL,13,     GHotel in Blackpool, run by
OL,14,     GAllison and Dave. The decor takes
OL,15,     GJake and Chris back to their
OL,16,     Gchildhood, but Celia and Damon
OL,17,     Garen't fans of the 1980s look.
